# Deploy — Lüdecker

## SSOT

| Fact | Location |
|------|----------|
| Render service name | `ludecker-website` |
| Blueprint | `render.yaml` at repo root |
| Production smoke URL | `https://ludecker-website.onrender.com/` |
| Deploy flow | Push to `main` → Render auto-build → Cloudflare → production |

## Ship commands

- `/release-app` or `/ship-ludecker` — AAAC release swarm (git → Render)
- Never force-push `main` unless user explicitly requests
- Never commit `.env`, `.env.local`, or service role keys

## Render MCP

Use **`user-render`** only. Service id from `list_services` where `name === "ludecker-website"`.

Poll deploy until `status === "live"` or report failure with build logs.
